article.headline: Ethan Roberts scores 25, Pennsylvania downs Maryland-Eastern Shore 87-84
article.description: — Ethan Roberts scored 25 points to help Pennsylvania defeat Maryland-Eastern Shore 87-84 on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Ethan Roberts scores 25, Pennsylvania downs Maryland-Eastern Shore 87-84
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Ethan Roberts scored 25 points to help Pennsylvania defeat Maryland-Eastern Shore 87-84 on Thursday night. Roberts had 10 rebounds for the Quakers (2-0). Sam Brown scored 22 points while shooting 5 for 15 (4 for 10 from 3-point range) and 8 of 8 from the free-throw line. George Smith shot 4 of 5 from the field and 5 of 7 from the free-throw line to finish with 14 points. Ketron Shaw led the Hawks (0-2) in scoring, finishing with 24 points, nine rebounds and five assists. Chris Flippin added 20 points and 13 rebounds. Kyrell Shaw had 16 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
